data.title: Rain Phoenix Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Rain Phoenix with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Spent much of her early life as part of the Children of God religious sect, in which her parents were missionaries

Made her film debut at age 15 in Maid to Order

Was a backup singer for the Red Hot Chili Peppers

Cofounded the Gift Horse Project with A

J

Mason to raise awareness and funds for artist-related charities

Vice president of the River Phoenix Center for Peacebuilding
